It‚Äôs honestly taken me a while to write this. The new term is starting back soon and I need to make some changes. The last term has been the hardest of my life so far - moving to a new country and being unable to make any lasting‚Ä¶ More relationships or new friendships has just been weighing on me constantly. I never felt as lonely or as isolated before despite not being very happy throughout school either. Whilst I am finding studying law monotonously dull and slightly soul destroying and not properly taking part in any societies which provide any light relief (deffo not law soc)! Sorry for the rant but I am just really desperate to make a positive change this term or I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôll be here for the next one. I would love any suggestions or helpful advice just really struggling right now x
